SPRING BOOT TESTS:

*UNIT TESTS
-we can use: @ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)
-Spring context not initialized
-shorter test execution time
-we can use standard Mockito annotations (@Mock, @InjectedMocks etc.)

*INTEGRATION TESTS
-use @SpringBootTest
-Spring context initialized
-Longer test execution time
-Use @MockBean to replace beans with mocked beans

______________________________________________
1. Mockito 5 requires Java 11 or higher.

2. Mockito 5 uses mockito-inline by default.